  &lt;p id="YPEhkH"&gt;If you’ve worked hard this year, you deserve to play even harder, and you can do that on a modest budget with some of the Prime Day gaming deals available right now. &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/24191617/amazon-prime-day-tech-deals-guide-2024"&gt;Amazon’s Prime Day 2024 sale&lt;/a&gt; is currently live and offers plenty of discounts on video games, controllers, headsets, storage, and other gear and accessories to level up your experience.&lt;/p&gt;
